description:
I’m kind, caring, hardworking and take pride in what I do.
I'm just an ordinary, down to earth and loving person but straight forward. 
I'm in no rush for a relationship, just to chat and see where it goes. 
I spend most my FREE time with my kids and at times with family for a braai etc.…I don’t do clubbing or pubs.
I’m not into SEX CHATS SO PLEASE KEEP YOU CHATS CLEAN if you really want to get to know me genuinely.
Last but not least…this is a dating site not a ATM
